newsitem.title: USA: CBOT overnight Project A ag volume 1,140 contracts.
newsitem.headline: CBOT overnight Project A ag volume 1,140 contracts.

text.p: The Chicago Board of Trade Project A overnight agricultural trading volume totalled 1,140 contracts compared with 1,380 overnight Wednesday, according to the CBOT.
There were 92 wheat, 571 corn, 294 soybean, one soymeal, 150 soyoil, two oat, seven rice, five wheat calls, eight corn calls, four corn puts and six soybean puts traded.
In overnight trading, wheat was 1/4 cent higher to 1/2 cent lower, corn was 1/4 to 3/4 cent higher and soybeans were 5-1/2 cents higher to 3/4 lower.
